	<section class="egrid egrid-2 mt-100 separator-horizontal separator-before" style="padding-top:100px">
		<div>
			<h2>All data at one place</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Stakers.space account let's you keep all data related to all your servers and validators under your management at one place.</li>
				<li>You can use Stakers.space dashboard as a privacy staking hub for you, your friends, family and clients. All see only relevant data for them. It means you can simply share individual instances data with clients or friends you manage them for. They just see only their validators and servers their validators are on.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<div class="tabselector">
                <nav class="egrid egrid-2">
